summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 26213 entitled: "An ordinance providing for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of certain portions of block 74, in the Plat of Lake Union Shore Lands, in the City of Seattle, for a site for City Stables, and providing for the payment of said property and for the cost of the necessary condemnation proceedings", approved January 30, 1911.
